room_title: Escape room "Spoopy's Ghoulish Graveyard Gameshow" by Doldrick's Escape Room in Orlando
room_description:
Lights! Camera! ACTION!

Players! Come on down! You're the next contestants on: Spoopy's Ghoulish Graveyard Games! Join Spoopy Bones LIVE on Stage as you work your way through the Ghoulish Graveyard! Do you have what it takes?
This escape game is suitable for the whole family! This episode of the Graveyard Games will take place in...you guessed it...a graveyard! Filmed in front of a "live studio audience", this game features immersive and incredible high-tech surprises!
